    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a reliable parts car? This vehicle is in poor condition and will need some dedicated mechanical attention and TLC to get it back to its best, but it offers a fantastic opportunity for a savvy buyer looking for a bargain! It\u2019s an honest, high-potential find for anyone who loves a good restoration challenge.",
