    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. It has been well-maintained, and all mechanical systems are fully operational. There are minor signs of cosmetic wear on the interior and exterior consistent with regular use.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong finish, though you may find a few minor stone chips and a small door ding consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is very clean with no tears in the upholstery and all electronic features functioning exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is solid, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has received regular oil changes and service. It is a dependable vehicle that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who isn't bothered by some cosmetic imperfections. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some clear coat peeling on the roof. Inside, the cabin is functional, though the driver\u2019s seat shows significant bolster wear and there are some persistent stains on the rear carpet. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, but the buyer should be aware that the brakes are squeaking and the suspension feels a bit loose, suggesting some maintenance will be required soon. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done without any frills.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly pristine condition. This exceptional example has been meticulously maintained to a collector-grade standard, appearing as though it just departed the showroom floor. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched, premium interior, every detail reflects an uncompromising commitment to excellence. For the sophisticated driver who demands the absolute pinnacle of quality and preservation, this vehicle stands as the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride of their life. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and polishing it until it shines like a mirror. It drives like an absolute dream, smooth as silk and ready for a weekend getaway. There might be a tiny, barely-there speck from the road here or there, but honestly, you\u2019d have to squint to find them. It\u2019s as close to perfect as they come! Come by, have a coffee, and let's get you behind the wheel.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine E92 M3, a true purist\u2019s specimen featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated V8. This vehicle has been maintained to a rigorous standard, with the common failure points proactively addressed; rod bearings have been swapped for VAC coated units with ARP hardware, and throttle actuators have been upgraded with uprated gears for lifetime reliability. The DCT transmission logic is crisp, delivering lightning-fast shifts with zero hesitation or slippage. The suspension geometry remains factory-tight, benefiting from refreshed bushings and a recent four-wheel laser alignment. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, protected by a multi-stage paint correction and 9H ceramic coating. This is a turn-key, apex-ready machine for the collector who demands mechanical perfection and high-revving performance. No subframe issues, no leaks, just pure Bavarian engineering at its peak.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Showroom condition. Zero flaws. Better than new. Priced to move fast. No tire kickers.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Slide behind the wheel and let the world outside dissolve into a blur of chrome and nostalgia. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a captured moment in time, finished in a deep, midnight gloss that swallows the moonlight. Every stitch in the saddle-leather interior whispers stories of coastal drives and sun-drenched afternoons. The engine doesn't just start; it awakens with a throaty, rhythmic pulse that resonates in your chest, promising a symphony of mechanical perfection. To own this is to curate a masterpiece, a pristine relic of an era when driving was an art form. It awaits a pilot who understands that some legends don't just age\u2014they transcend.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This unit remains in pristine showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained to preserve its original luster and mechanical integrity. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, every detail reflects a history of uncompromising care. For the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just left the factory floor, this offering represents an unparalleled value proposition and a rare opportunity to own a vehicle of this caliber.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    }
  ],
